---
import Header from "../../components/company/CompanyHeader.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/company/CompanyFooter.astro";

const EFFECTIVE_DATE = "November 10, 2025";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Privacy Policy & Terms • CityGuessr</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Privacy Policy and Terms of Service for CityGuessr by Ashak Studios." />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#8D46E7" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" />

    <!-- Inter (serious, clean) -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

    <!-- Ensure Header/Footer also use Inter -->
    <style is:global>
      :root { --ff: 'Inter', ui-sans-serif, system-ui; }
    </style>

    <style>
      :root{
        --bg:#050507; --bg-2:#0C0D12;
        --panel:#0F1016; --panel-2:#131521;
        --text:#F2F2F7; --muted:#B8B9C8; --line:#232536;
        --brand:#8D46E7; --radius:16px; --shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.45)
      }
      *{box-sizing:border-box}
      html,body{
        margin:0; padding:0;
        background:radial-gradient(1200px 400px at 50% -10%, #121327 0%, transparent 60%), var(--bg);
        color:var(--text); font:16px/1.7 'Inter', ui-sans-serif, system-ui;
        scroll-behavior:smooth;
      }
      a{color:inherit}
      .container{max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 16px}
      .section{padding:56px 0}
      .hero{padding:72px 0 28px;text-align:center}
      .heading-1{font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.2px;font-size:clamp(24px,3.2vw,40px);line-height:1.15;margin:0}
      .kicker{color:var(--muted);font-weight:500;font-size:14px;margin:10px 0 0}

      .card{
        background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--panel),var(--panel-2));
        border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:var(--radius);
        box-shadow:var(--shadow); padding:20px;
      }
      .h2{font-size:clamp(20px,2.2vw,28px);font-weight:700;margin:0 0 8px}
      .h3{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;margin:16px 0 6px}
      .meta{font-size:13px;color:#C9CAE2}
      .list{margin:8px 0 0 18px}
      .list li{margin:4px 0}
      .sep{height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,#262944,transparent);margin:24px 0}
      .toc{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;margin-top:14px}
      .chip{font-size:13px;padding:6px 10px;border-radius:999px;border:1px solid #2D3050;background:#12142A;color:#E7E7F4;font-weight:600}
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="heading-1">Privacy Policy & Terms of Service — CityGuessr</h1>
        <p class="kicker">Effective Date: {EFFECTIVE_DATE}</p>
        <div class="toc">
          <a class="chip" href="#/privacy">Go to Privacy Policy</a>
          <a class="chip" href="#/terms">Go to Terms of Service</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PRIVACY POLICY -->
    <section id="/privacy" class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
          <h2 class="h2">Privacy Policy</h2>
          <div class="meta">Applies to: “CityGuessr” for iOS and Android, published by Ashak Studios.</div>

          <h3 class="h3">1) Summary</h3>
          <p>
            CityGuessr is built to respect your privacy. We do not run player accounts and we do not collect or store
            personal data on Ashak Studios servers. App preferences are stored locally on your device.
          </p>

          <h3 class="h3">2) Data We Do <em>Not</em> Collect or Store</h3>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>No names, email addresses, phone numbers, or passwords</li>
            <li>No precise location data</li>
            <li>No advertising SDKs and <strong>no advertisements of any kind</strong></li>
            <li>No analytics/telemetry or crash profiling SDKs run by Ashak Studios</li>
            <li>No retention of device identifiers or IP addresses by Ashak Studios</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="h3">3) Local-Only App Data</h3>
          <p>
            The game keeps limited settings on-device (e.g., language, sound, UI preferences and any purchase receipts
            stored by the platform). Removing the app from your device removes these records.
          </p>

          <h3 class="h3">4) Payments (No Accounts, No External Tracking)</h3>
          <p>
            CityGuessr offers optional <strong>one-time support purchases</strong> (donations). Payments are processed by
            Apple’s App Store (iOS) or Google Play (Android). We do not receive your full payment details and we do not
            run our own payment servers. There are <strong>no subscriptions</strong> and <strong>no ads</strong>.
          </p>

          <h3 class="h3">5) Children’s Privacy</h3>
          <p>
            If you are under the age required by local law to make purchases or provide consent, please use the game with
            a parent or guardian.
          </p>

          <h3 class="h3">6) Connectivity</h3>
          <p>
            The game can open offline. Purchase validation may require an internet connection; when offline, status may
            not refresh until connectivity is restored.
          </p>

          <h3 class="h3">7) Changes to This Policy</h3>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy as products or requirements change. If updated, the new version will
            replace this one and the “Effective Date” above will be revised.
          </p>

          <h3 class="h3">8) Contact</h3>
          <p>
            Questions about privacy may be sent to <a href="mailto:contact@ashak.co">contact@ashak.co</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TERMS OF SERVICE -->
    <section id="/terms" class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
          <h2 class="h2">Terms of Service</h2>
          <div class="meta">Effective Date: {EFFECTIVE_DATE}</div>

          <h3 class="h3">1) About These Terms</h3>
          <p>
            These Terms govern your use of CityGuessr for iOS and Android, published by Ashak Studios (“we,” “us”).
            By installing or using the game, you agree to these Terms.
          </p>

          <h3 class="h3">2) License</h3>
          <p>
            We grant you a personal, limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable license to use the game on
            compatible devices for entertainment. You may not reverse engineer, redistribute, or commercially exploit the game.
          </p>

          <h3 class="h3">3) Advertising</h3>
          <p>
            CityGuessr contains <strong>no advertisements</strong>.
          </p>

          <h3 class="h3">4) Purchases (One-Time Donations)</h3>
          <ul class="list">
            <li><strong>Optional, one-time support:</strong> The in-app “support” tiers are voluntary donations and <em>do not unlock gameplay features</em>.</li>
            <li><strong>Platform Processing:</strong> Payments are processed by Apple App Store or Google Play. Manage receipts or request refunds per the platform’s policies.</li>
            <li><strong>No Subscriptions:</strong> CityGuessr does not offer subscriptions or auto-renewing products.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="h3">5) Third-Party Services</h3>
          <p>
            Aside from platform billing (Apple App Store / Google Play), CityGuessr does not integrate advertising,
            analytics, tracking, or crash-profiling SDKs.
          </p>

          <h3 class="h3">6) Connectivity</h3>
          <p>
            Some payment functions require internet access. If offline, purchase status may be unavailable until
            connectivity is restored.
          </p>

          <h3 class="h3">7) Warranties & Liability</h3>
          <p>
            The game is provided “as is” and “as available.” To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, we disclaim
            warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, and non-infringement, and we limit liability
            to the maximum extent permitted by law.
          </p>

          <h3 class="h3">8) Changes to These Terms</h3>
          <p>
            We may revise these Terms when features or requirements change. Continued use after changes constitutes
            acceptance of the updated Terms.
          </p>

          <h3 class="h3">9) Contact</h3>
          <p>
            For support or legal questions, contact: <a href="mailto:contact@ashak.co">contact@ashak.co</a>
          </p>

          <div class="sep"></div>
          <p class="meta">Quick navigation: <a href="#/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> • <a href="#/terms">Terms of Service</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
